<tr>
<td style=" vertical-align: top;">
<a href="http://en.blog.wordpress.com/author/ericarenaejohnson/" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" title="http://en.blog.wordpress.com/author/ericarenaejohnson/" target="_blank"></a>
